flowchart LR
    Root["<b>SageOS-RV/rtos/</b>"]
    
    Root --> Sub["<b>SageRTOS/</b><br/><i>(git submodule)</i>"]
    Root --> GlueH["sagertos_glue.h<br/><i>kernel-facing API shim</i>"]
